c: 12
v: 19
t: "Omukanda kwali khuluchendo nikuula, nibaruma omutayi wabu wa amatsi, mana natombola indo yiyie mulitikho lia amatsi (eshisima), naboola mbu ; “obulayi buli burie buno, khuli nomwana omusiani hano! Nibamufisa okhumukhola omusiko- (Kweyinganga). Ne Nyasaye ni Omumanyi wakoosi kamukholanga"